wikipedia_page.main: Martin Atkins (born 24 December 1965) is an English professional darts player. His nickname is The Assassin.

response: Martin Atkins (born 4 April 1975) is an English darts player who competes for the Professional Darts Corporation. He is sometimes referred to as Martin Atkins (Wigan) to avoid confusion with another player named Martin Atkins, who comes from Leeds.
* Martin Atkins (born 1959), English drummer and session musician
* Martin Atkins (darts player, born 1965), English professional darts player
* Martin Atkins (darts player, born 1975), English professional darts player
